Sistemnye trebovanija: 
Operacionnaja sistema Windows 95/98/ME/NT/2000/XP
Processor AMD Athlon ili Intel Pentium III 450 MGc i vyshe;
Operativnaja pamjat&amp;#039; 128 MB;
Video Nvidia TNT Series/GeForce Series, ATI Rage 128/Radeon, 3dfx Voodoo5, Matrox G400;
Zvuk EAX ili A3D sovmestimaja zvukovaja karta;
